def prod(s1, s2):
    if not s1 or not s2:
        return "0"

    s1, s2 = s1.strip(), s2.strip()
    neg = s1[0] == '-' ^ s2[0] == '-'
    s1, s2 = s1[1:], s2[1:] if neg else s1, s2[1:]

    if len(s1) > len(s2):
        s1, s2 = s2, s1

    carry = 0
    res = ""
    for i in range(len(s1)-1, -1, -1):
        p1 = ord(s1[i]) - ord('0')
        mul = carry
        for j in range(len(s2)):
            p2 = ord(s2[j]) - ord('0')
            prod = p1 * p2 + mul
            mul = prod // 10
            prod %= 10
            res += str(prod)
        if mul:
            res += str(mul)

    if neg:
        res = "-" + res
    return res[::-1]

assert prod("123", "456") == "56088"
assert prod("12", "45") == "540"
assert prod("123", "9") == "1107"
assert prod("0", "45") == "0"
assert prod("123", "0") == "0"
assert prod("-123", "45") == "-5535"
assert prod("123", "-45") == "-5535"
assert prod("-123", "-45") == "5535"
